Get the id of the last model ran

This function returns the model ids for the last number models saved to leaderboard. This function is intended to be used with peak.

at_last(number = 1)

Arguments

number

number that indicates the last n models to peak at.

Value

model id of last models

Examples

# peak at previous model
board() %>%
  peak(at_last())
